reviewText:
I love this band so much! Love this show.
The only problem is that the discs do not play on my Samsung UBD-8500K Player. Dissapointed but atleast i can see it on my computer.
If you are a huge fan you must buy this show!
It came open,missing the booklet but I love the band soo much that I didn't care. It is very hard to find this dvd,so over all I am happy
